               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17470429-38-off166-c327" targOrder="Y" targets="t17470429-38-defend402 t17470429-38-off166 t17470429-38-verdict168"></join>
         
               <p>226. 
               
                  <persName id="t17470429-38-defend402" type="defendantName">
                     Esther 
                     Gooding 
                  <interp inst="t17470429-38-defend402" type="surname" value="Gooding"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470429-38-defend402" type="given" value="Esther"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470429-38-defend402" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17470429-38-off166" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17470429-38-off166" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470429-38-off166" type="offenceSubcategory" value="other"></interp>
               stealing one Pair of Linen Sheets
            </rs>, the Goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17470429-38-victim404" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Gundy 
                  <interp inst="t17470429-38-victim404" type="surname" value="Gundy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470429-38-victim404" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470429-38-victim404" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17470429-38-off166 t17470429-38-victim404"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17470429-38-cd167" type="crimeDate">March 22</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17470429-38-off166 t17470429-38-cd167"></join>.</p>
               <p>The Prosecutor, 
               <persName id="t17470429-38-person405">
                  Thomas 
                  Gundy 
               <interp inst="t17470429-38-person405" type="surname" value="Gundy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470429-38-person405" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17470429-38-person405" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , appeared to be rigorous to the poor Woman about these Sheets, but the Court had Information that his Conduct in letting his Lodgings was very blameable , for he had, by his own Confession, four Beds in his Room, and let them at so much a Night to Men and Women, all in a promiscuous Manner.</p>
               <p>The Court sharply admonished him, and <rs id="t17470429-38-verdict168" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17470429-38-verdict168" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               acquitted
            </rs> the Prisoner, who, though poor, had a better Character than himself.</p>
